<p class="MsoNormal">Established in 1993,
Beidahu Ski Resort is situated at southwest of Jilin. Thanks to the short
distance of 53km to the city, Beidahu Ski Resort has become a multi-function
centre for competition, training, tourism, fitness and recuperation. </p><p class="MsoNormal">It has
staged many skiing events including the 8th National Winter Games, the 9th
National Winter Games, and the 6th Asian Winter Games. </p>